        <!--
          Release workflow:
          1. Archive in Xcode → export notarized .dmg
          2. Sign the DMG:
               find ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData -name sign_update | head -1
               /path/to/sign_update Crosscheck-X.Y.Z.dmg
             → copy edSignature and length from output
          3. Add an <item> below (copy the template, fill in version/date/signature/length/URL)
          4. git commit docs/appcast.xml && git push → GitHub Pages serves it automatically
          5. Upload .dmg to https://github.com/bencolson/Crosscheck/releases as a Release asset
        -->

    </channel>
</rss>
